Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.04,0:00:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,榮依子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.94,0:00:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,榮依子?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.42,0:00:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.84,0:02:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,換夏裝了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.84,0:02:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,耶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.72,0:02:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,一大早就吃冰淇淋…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.29,0:02:34.78,Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(825.429,582)}{\fad(500,500)\c&H9D65DE&\bord2\blur1}Step5 「冠的毛茸茸」
