Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.02,0:20:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,「空氣」這種行為就不再僅僅是慣用句了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.70,0:20:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,居然要實際操作
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.62,0:20:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,受教了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.02,0:20:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,花…小花名
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.43,0:21:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,原來如此 受教了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.34,0:21:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我覺得不是這麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.94,0:22:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,小冠 早安
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.60,0:22:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 早安
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.64,0:22:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.60,0:22:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,貓
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.34,0:22:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.44,0:22:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,來這邊來這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.08,0:23:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,榮依子很擅長讓貓親近自己
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.88,0:23:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.40,0:23:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,榮依子好厲害啊
