Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.44,0:23:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,小冠也超級黏榮依子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.76,0:23:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,那…那個 對…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.32,0:23:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.48,0:23:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,啊
